casebody.data:
ALABAMA DEMOCRATIC CONFERENCE, et al., appellants,
v.
ALABAMA, et al. No. 13-1138. Supreme Court of the United States June 2, 2014.

*2698Appeals from the United States District Court for the Middle District of Alabama. In this case probable jurisdiction noted limited to Question 2 presented by the statement as to jurisdiction in No. 13-895 and Question 1 presented by the statement as to jurisdiction in No. 13-1138. The case is consolidated and a total of one hour is allotted for oral argument.
